{"tid":1244108,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[好唔好玩?] 快閃團隊遊戲","createTime":"2019-06-19T18:03:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T14:16:26.000Z","uid":239351,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb893eac9d46b29e6c2243dc259f16f3c6eaff1b","tid":1244108,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:03:20.000Z","msg":"遊戲玩法好簡單<br />\n<br />\n首先參加者自己組合8-10人為一組. 由於遊戲範圍較大, 每一組必需一同行動, 以免有人走失.<br />\n遊戲開始時, 各組可於不同地點向不同方向走. 當兩組遇上時, 兩組務必在路上停下最多三分鐘. 三分鐘後向不同方向停下. 遊戲中有角色會捉拿停下來的小組, 他們也組成8-10人小隊. 因此, 遇上壞人時亦可以繼續行走. <br />\n<br />\n遊戲的參加者是同一隊的. 計分方法則是計算總停頓時間, 減去被壞人追拿的人數.<br />\n<br />\n註, 此為戶外遊戲, 參加者需帶備足夠食水. 另外請留意交通規則."},{"pid":"f9a1b3e6cda8b845ea9c1fc09d2075b0f9c71702","tid":1244108,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:03:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5ea7e9ef8daf46864ea8ebc9dd034cd5a5fc5315","tid":1244108,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:08:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"206a00118981b66bcda5fea481a68b2f7dfc248c","tid":1244108,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:16:00.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dbc50bb3af59ca0c0370a2cee7f685fde0df0835","tid":1244108,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T18:21:41.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6d8341dbb826433a2c6c48a45264eb684bc87a2a","tid":1244108,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:48:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"92f51c842aec10230b39bcb6843d097bd6f3fe59","tid":1244108,"uid":13467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T00:49:33.000Z","msg":"連登仔呢？"},{"pid":"d0040c570bf430da122dd7268c2c852837fa1310","tid":1244108,"uid":239351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T02:16:37.000Z","msg":"好唔好玩都話我知"},{"pid":"b23e384225dbbf6f614956a6def69c4c827581fa","tid":1244108,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply